    "raw": "The tags from the various musicology services have varied domain. But each service is internally consistent. We want to come up with a synonym mapping so that all tags are in the same domain.  Then we want to categorize them into  <type>|<value>.  (these tags are surfaced as dir names, so cannot contain samba-excluded chars like ':').  types : artist, album, year, genre, collection.  values: petergabriel, so, 1984, 1980s, pop poprock, djkicks (all examples).   The synonym mapping will be per source, generated by an llm agent scanning all the values.  It will further investigate each provider's data, so that we can derive types where not clear, and paths in the returned documentsfor deterministic extraction of album data.   The goal is that the LLM prepare the data for mechanistic evalution."
  },
